Another for catarrh and cough of any kind. Take hyssop and dry the leaves in the sun and then make powder and eat this in the morning or drink it with wine or water while fasting up to the tierce. In this way you will be helped.

Another for cough. Take 1 lb. of juice of red cabbage and boil it and skim it and take Â½ lb. of skimmed and strained honey and put everything together to boil and put in 1 dram of saffron and 1 dram of tragacanth gum and boil all together until the juice is consumed. The amount of a bean is taken on an empty stomach and it should be allowed to melt in the mouth.

